name: Study Timer
body:
## What is Study Timer? ##

It is a desktop application that will track your study time. 
Set up the title of your study session (i.e. "Math assignment") and a duration.
Your study sessions will be saved into a text file.

Download and run the program: https://goo.gl/8rAXTR
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
